<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Moderator Application Result - Not Approved</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
      }
      .reason {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Moderator Application Result</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear Applicant,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for your interest in becoming a moderator for our platform.
          After careful review of your application, we regret to inform you that
          we are unable to approve your request at this time.
        </p>

        <div class="reason">
          <p><strong>Reason:</strong></p>
          <p><%= comment %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          While we cannot proceed with your application at this moment, we
          encourage you to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Continue being an active member of our community</li>
          <li>
            Consider applying again after addressing the mentioned concerns
          </li>
          <li>Reach out to our support team if you need any clarification</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          We appreciate your understanding and your commitment to our academic
          community.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help? Contact us at <%= supportEmail %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
